responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "0D2340424894A7C0A4FC428747E5EE1D", "That\'s not all, my friend. Eudoxia was unable to assure the destruction of the Roots of Erantia, the magic wards on the perimeter of what was Thanalas. She asked me to find someone to eliminate those that hope to sever the arcane roots. Who better than you?")
